        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Energy Sovereignty Act</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Clean Air Act to prohibit the Environmental Protection Agency from requiring states to prevent or eliminate air pollution endangering public health or welfare in other countries.</p>]]></text>
